&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;# 5. Deploy to GitHub Pages (automatically push public directory to gh-pages branch)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
